可能&quot; <span style=\"color: red;\">觸犯為境外非法提供情報罪</span><br />\n2. 桂敏海 專&quot;自己&quot; 登恢復中國國籍等自己可以坐10年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3fcd6e54477ccd3f3b0cc1d7d3f36a6666e0f5a","tid":1896444,"uid":138064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"736b007eaeba59a44786a6bc2c83ce751dd76bb3","tid":1896444,"uid":140984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:01:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6f0b375859dd818e4ca12dff10af50415f170db6","tid":1896444,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c6aea24809849ef7de8cc2d6036d75c0a2a088b","tid":1896444,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:45:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n仲要係泰國捉走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:02:24.000Z","msg":"泰國政府實有協助<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3011396fe332b2e0b4761b3028863637a3b599","tid":1896444,"uid":140984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:08:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fcd7650a04d961d0cb918c88dbac39a05cbf6131","tid":1896444,"uid":119232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:11:20.000Z","msg":"可話呢個世界得返美國可以叫安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1fb3ab5488a55996af24724ea3a90c98530507","tid":1896444,"uid":16109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:17:07.000Z","msg":"即係官媒認證佢出書既資料都係真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"80f6179ffacd728a6893fbf79d0313757d16b9f7","tid":1896444,"uid":140984,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"入左瑞典國籍 共狗強行幫佢恢復中國國籍<br />\nSrc: <a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-51624603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Fsimp%2Fchinese-news-51624603&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=332988ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Fsimp%2Fchinese-news-51624603&h=9be795a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-51624603</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">桂敏海表示认罪服判不上诉。并称1996年加入瑞典国籍的桂敏海&ldquo;2018年经其本人申请依法恢复中国国籍&rdquo;。</code></pre>"}}